\begin_inset Formula $x+\dot{x}\frac{v}{1\dot{z}}+\ddot{x}\frac{v^{2}}{1\cdot2\dot{z}^{2}}+\dddot{x}\frac{v^{3}}{1\cdot2\cdot3\dot{z}^{3}}+\mbox{\&c}$
